SUMMARY:Montclair Public Library Talk | Famous Pharaohs: Egypt’s Legendary Leaders and Their Monuments
DESCRIPTION:Meet Egypt’s most legendary rulers: Tutankhamun\, Ramses the Great\, Hatshepsut\, and more. Explore the monuments\, temples\, and tombs that preserve their stories\, as we journey to iconic sites including the pyramids of Giza\, the magnificent temples of Luxor and Abu Simbel\, and the royal tombs in the Valley of the Kings. \nPresented by Montclair Public Library Adult School. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
