SUMMARY:C3Workplace/C3Worx presents: From Interest to Impact: A Better Buying Funnel
DESCRIPTION:The rise of AI has changed how buyers interact with brands. Prospects are now coming to the table with more context than ever before. A single AI search can shape how they evaluate options long before a first conversation. \nThe path from initial interest to signed deal looks different now. Outbound\, inbound\, nurture\, automation\, and sales execution are still part of the equation. What’s changing is how those pieces work together as buyers move through the funnel in less predictable ways. \nJoin us on March 10 at 12 pm ET for a virtual panel discussion with experts across the full buying funnel who will share how teams are adapting their go-to-market approach as buyer behavior evolves. \nThe 60-minute Business Growth Roundtable will cover:\nOutbound sales and marketing approaches that earn attention and garner engagement\nInbound strategies that attract high-intent buyers\nLead nurturing tactics that turn interest into sales conversations\nPractical ways teams are using AI to scale execution while preserving human judgment\nSales enablement approaches that shorten sales cycles and increase close rates \nWho Should Attend\nB2B and professional services marketing and sales leaders\nRevenue\, demand gen\, and growth leaders responsible for pipeline and sales performance\nTeams looking to better connect marketing strategy\, technology\, and sales execution \nRegister here.\nhttps://us02web.zoom.us/webinar/register/2017690106090/WN_X71qoxR_TNarAygFwXKYGA#/registration \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
